intro: A Crazy Brotherly Airborne Fighting Game
description:
The third game in the legendary Cho Aniki series created by Masaya. The fighting game Cho Aniki: Bakuretsu Ranto Hen has been fully ported for the Nintendo Switch™.
Eight unique characters compete in the First World Martial Arts Tournament hosted by the planet NCS Super Masayan. Who will emerge victorious?
Additional features such as Audio, Cutscenes, and Rewind are also available to enjoy this masterpiece to the fullest.
A must-have for retro game fans and fighting game fans alike.
